Something dangerous lurks in the sewers today. He does not know what caused his mutation, but when Crawk woke up, he woke up hungry, so if you hear a splashing down below the city manholes, you best not go and investigate. The human crocodile has claimed this as his domain. The set comes complete with custom crafted High Definition Morphs, and a highly detailed texture set, suitable for Iray and 3Delight
